Package IOinterface

Class StandardGameView

java.lang.Object
IOinterface.StandardGameView
All Implemented Interfaces:
GameView
public class StandardGameView extends Object implements GameView
This is the standard implementation of GameView. This uses the terminal for printing the game. Note that this may have some problem on non Unix platforms since it uses escape chars for colors.
